Spring based on Dependency injection-  automatic creation of object and injecting that into required place.
IOC- inversion of control

main modules provided  by Spring
Core, beans, context, spEl

steps to create Spring App
1. create maven project
2. add spring dependencies
3 Create bean class POJO
4. create config file
    a . add beans and other properties as required.
5. Create Application Context
6 retrieve the object (inside mqain class with the help of ApplicationvContext Obj)

Config file
XML file where we declare the beans and its dependencies


Application Context
1. AnnotationConfigApplicationContext
2.ClassPathXMLApplicationContext
3 FileSystemXMLApplicationContext

ways of dependency injection
1 Setter injection
2 Constructor injection


spEL
#{<any expression>}
#{T(class).method(param)}

#{T(class).variable
#{ new java.lang.String('hello')}